title: [Mairiseth Telearat, Courtyard]
description: Colorful clusters of artwork are arranged between resaeun easels along the faenor-forged railings, the supported frames shaded beneath heartleaf-canopied pergolas.  Long velvet-padded chairs rest alongside each easel, each one angled towards the waters below.  Floral-draped lanterns flank the descending pathway, the faerthiel-decorated spheres faintly illuminating the rooftop gardens below.
